srcDoc.html:
Customer App for Business Central

The Customer App is a portal where customers can view their financial transactions from Business Central, then can log in and see their invoices, credit notes, payments, and refunds


About Appamith Solution for Business Central

Appamith Solution is a Business Central App that provides login, token, and API infrastructure for Appmith apps.
